name: amanda Register
text: Well it's a shame it takes a bad incident for me to write this review but sadly now I must. So far the pizzas have been awesome, I love they are quick and ready in no time from store to home. Would have been perfect for a rainy night like â€¦More

name: Cattle with Kati
text: Workers are friendly and fast. Dough is always fresh, tasty, and fluffy. Easy to bake and doesn't take long.

name: Savannah Howell Knoblaugh
text: For those who are low income and want to have a special pizza night with the family they do take EBT.

name: L Nalley
text: The staff are always great and the pizza is even better!

name: Tammara Gill
text: AHMAZING Pizza! The taco Pizza  (seasonal) is awesome.  It's our favorite!! Thank you for coming to Lake City! HALLELUJAH!!!

name: Richard Carby
text: Lake City we are fortunate to have been given the best way to have pizza at home, you are going to be hooked.

name: Chris Benford
text: Great pizza at a great price! No place to eat inside, its strictly take and bake.
